        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2707454148" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5367450536847904221">This is a unique book. Very different from what I was expecting, but pleasing. Major Victor Cornwall and Major St. John Trevelyan bounce off each other in this funny compelling read. It is the memoirs of there time as spies, with murder, adventure, tragedy and deceit. It has its uplifting and heartfelt moments as well. I really enjoyed this! 5 stars!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


